  - contactName: Leo
    messages:
    - sender: Leo
      content: "Heii, scuze c\u0103 te deranjez aiurea, dar tu ai f\u0103cut info,
        nu?"
      isOldConversation: 0
      isDecision: 0
      wasRead: 0
      wasDecisionTaken: 0
      choices: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: da... de ce?=))
      isOldConversation: 0
      isDecision: 0
      wasRead: 0
      wasDecisionTaken: 0
      choices: []
    - sender: Leo
      content: "Am un curs op\u021Bional de Structuri de Date \u0219i n-am \xEEn\u021Beles
        nimic azi la lab. Po\u021Bi s\u0103-mi explici ce-i aia list\u0103 dublu
        \xEEnl\u0103n\u021Buit\u0103?"
      isOldConversation: 0
      isDecision: 0
      wasRead: 0
      wasDecisionTaken: 0
      choices: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: "(\u3063 \u0361 \u0361\xBA - \u0361 \u0361\xBA \u03C2)"
      isOldConversation: 0
      isDecision: 0
      wasRead: 0
      wasDecisionTaken: 0
      choices: []
    - sender: Leo
      content: "Adic\u0103\u2026 cum naiba se mut\u0103 pointerele alea? C\u0103
        am impresia c\u0103 profesorul vorbea klingonian\u0103."
      isOldConversation: 0
      isDecision: 0
      wasRead: 0
      wasDecisionTaken: 0
      choices: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: "G\xE2nde\u0219te-te la o instala\u021Bie de art\u0103 dintr-un coridor
        lung."
      isOldConversation: 0
      isDecision: 0
      wasRead: 0
      wasDecisionTaken: 0
      choices: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: "Pe fiecare perete sunt ag\u0103\u021Bate sculpturi, \u0219i \xEEntre
        ele exist\u0103 fire vizibile care le conecteaz\u0103 \u2014 unul spre sculptura
        anterioar\u0103, altul spre urm\u0103toarea."
      isOldConversation: 0
      isDecision: 0
      wasRead: 0
      wasDecisionTaken: 0
      choices: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: "Dac\u0103 vrei s\u0103 adaugi o sculptur\u0103 nou\u0103 \xEEntre
        dou\u0103 existente, trebuie s\u0103 mu\u021Bi firele \u2014 s\u0103 tai
        leg\u0103tura dintre cele dou\u0103 vechi \u0219i s\u0103 legi noua pies\u0103
        la ambele."
      isOldConversation: 0
      isDecision: 0
      wasRead: 0
      wasDecisionTaken: 0
      choices: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: "Asta e o list\u0103 dublu \xEEnl\u0103n\u021Buit\u0103: fiecare element
        \u201E\u0219tie\u201D de cine a fost \xEEnainte \u0219i de cine vine dup\u0103."
      isOldConversation: 0
      isDecision: 0
      wasRead: 0
      wasDecisionTaken: 0
      choices: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: "A\u0219a po\u021Bi merge \xEEn ambele direc\u021Bii prin \u201Eexpozi\u021Bie\u201D
        \u2014 \xEEnainte \u0219i \xEEnapoi \u2014 f\u0103r\u0103 s\u0103 pierzi
        vreun fir."
      isOldConversation: 0
      isDecision: 0
      wasRead: 0
      wasDecisionTaken: 0
      choices: []
    - sender: Leo
      content: "Ooohh damn, ok, acum chiar vizualizez.\nDeci dac\u0103 \u201Etai
        firele\u201D f\u0103r\u0103 grij\u0103, se pr\u0103bu\u0219e\u0219te expozi\u021Bia."
      isOldConversation: 0
      isDecision: 0
      wasRead: 0
      wasDecisionTaken: 0
      choices: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: "Exact. De asta e nevoie s\u0103 actualizezi leg\u0103turile, nu doar
        s\u0103 adaugi sculptura."
      isOldConversation: 0
      isDecision: 0
      wasRead: 0
      wasDecisionTaken: 0
      choices: []
    - sender: Leo
      content: "wow. de ce explic\u0103 nimeni lucrurile a\u0219a? e\u0219ti o legend\u0103"
      isOldConversation: 0
      isDecision: 0
      wasRead: 0
      wasDecisionTaken: 0
      choices: []
